Got the beautiful @battatawada holi ready for her recent campaign with @reliancetrends ❤️❤️

Posted @withregram • @battatawada Iss holi ko kuch khaas banane ko Trends laya hai ‘Holi ka Har Rang’. Aap Holi ki kisi bhi dhun pe apna Dancing ya Singing ka 1 minute tak ka video banaiye aur whatsapp kariye  9889899897 par ya upload karein apni entry www.trendsholikaharrang.com par. Sath hi video ko Facebook aur Instagram par #HoliKaHarRang ke sath share karein aur @reliancetrends & #DainikJagran tag karna na bhoole.
Agar aapki entry humein pasand aayi toh Aap jeet sakte hain 7 lakh rupaye tak ke  prizes  saath hi main aur @tahirrajbhasin aayeinge aapse milne aapke nazdeeki Shahar ke Trends Store par. #ad
